title: Yummba
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Was vegetarian but added meat to its menu as reported 2015. Fast food cafe at the university. Offers falafel, pita, dips, and salads. Note the bagels contain egg.
streetAddress: University Terraces B8, University of New South Wales
